author: Anonymouz
text: Minnesota Attorney General Ellison: Rescind the Minneapolis Medical Examiner’s report of George Floyd - Sign the Petition! https://t.co/EkvviujSWj via @Change

author: Anonymouz
text:
This message is right on time,because God knows I've been worrying& under stress,but I know he's able🙏🙏

Mikiah Keener Mini: God is fixing every situation you're worried about! Stop stressing about how it's going to happen & just trust that God will make it happen!

author: Anonymouz
text:
Right on time!!! #NeededThis 🙌🙌🙏🙏 #Amen

Mikiah Keener Mini: Remember, sometimes you have to go through the worst to get to the best! Push through the pain, because giving up will hurt more! Amen. ❤️

author: Anonymouz
text:

Mikiah Keener Mini: The most powerful thing u can do right now is to be patient and trust God while things are unfolding for you. Dont worry, it's coming! Amen.

text:

text:

text:

text:
